---
title: Caramelised Onion Chicken Burger with honey mustard mayo and crispy chips
description: This is a simple recipe made up of classic elements that go together oh so well. The winning combination of sweet and savoury can be seen in both the caramelised onion and the honey mustard mayo. Crispy chicken and crunchy chips are another perfect pairing in this delicious dish.
